    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "mdContentB",
      "x": 435,
      "y": 335,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 350,
      "text": "# Customer Support Guide\n\nWelcome to the Acme Corp customer support\nguide. This document covers common issues\nand their resolutions.\n\n## Getting Started\n\nBefore contacting support, please check\nthe FAQ section for quick answers to\ncommon questions.\n\n## Account Issues\n\nIf you're experiencing account-related\nproblems, follow these steps:\n\n1. Verify your email address\n2. Check your subscription status\n3. Reset your password if needed\n\n... (scrollable markdown content)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
